reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 28, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Read Reviews, Took a Chance, Super Satisfied
reviews.reviewText: I read that people rated this product badly because of the screen protector not fitting the screen and I was tentative about getting this brand, but I needed a protector so I gave it a shot.The case it comes in is convenient, like a hollow book, so you can store the extra alcohol wipes, dust stickers, screen protectors and glass cloth for later use easily. The instructions were easy to follow but my one disliking is nothing was labeled, I had to guess to figure out which had the alcohol wipe (it's the paperish packet btw). There was also some sort of plastic applicator guide thingy? But they dont reference it in the instructions, nor did I know how to use it. Bummer.After I cleaned it, I slipped the back sticker off the protector, making sure not to touch the inner side of it, and eyeballed where it should adhere to.The screen protector IS ONLY MEANT TO GO OVER THE PART OF THE SCREEN THAT LIGHTS UP. It can't go any more because the phone is rounded and I'm pretty sure that's why people rated this so low because they didn't know any better.I think I got it pretty spot on with only like 1/12 of an inch error but it's not noticeable at all. The screen protector will always look a little off because you can't cover an entire iPhone 11 screen with one but slap on a phone case and your eyes adjust easily.There was one tiny little bubble that formed that I can't get out of the dang underside which irritates me.Disclaimer: In the photos, there are little hair-line scratches but those are underneath the screen protector, my phone screen is covered in them (walmart refurbished standards *sigh*). But the screen protector fills out and hides 99% of them!! Added bonus! Just not all, but it's not a product defect it's my phone lol. ALSO, that weird screen discoloration was caused by taking a picture of a phone with another phone, no it does not look like that in real life, just photography error.I have read reviews about the screen protector being easily broken but for the low price I paid and the screen underneath being safe, it's worth the money. Plus you get 3 screen protectors, so if you chuck your phone into oblivion or you just fail that hard at applying it to your screen, you get 2 more chances.TLDR; Great product!! Would totally reccomend. 👌
